name: Tsalagi Basketweaving #5
description: A digitally rendered Tsalagi (Cherokee) basket weaving pattern. #5 of this series depicts pale purple, blue and white. Seven copies available for the seven clans. Artist: Kimberly Lollis-McCauley (Cherokee), 2021. Website: www.galonedi.com. Twitter: @galonedi. Instagram:@kimberly.lollis.mccauley. Facebook: Galonedi ᎦᎶᏁᏗ Studio
